description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15 Minute Energy Cleanse (Guided Meditation)' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Just 15 minutes to immerse yourself in this energy cleanse guided meditation can rejuvenate your mind, body, and spirit in profound ways.  We often accumulate stress, tension, and negative energy that weigh us down and cloud our clarity. This meditation offers a powerful tool to release these burdens, cleanse your energetic field, and restore balance within yourself.  Through gentle visualization and intentional breathing, you can let go of stagnant energy, emotional baggage, and mental clutter, creating space for renewed vitality and positivity to flow freely.  Reclaim your sense of peace, and step forward with a lighter, more vibrant energy that empowers you to navigate life's challenges with grace and resilience.  This is an Original 15 minute guided  morning meditation recorded by us.  

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!  
We appreciate all your support and contribution to allow this channel to continue to share our guided meditations with the world.  Thank you!!!
